comments: Green (LAL) initiates contact to Nurkic's (POR) body during the pick that dislodges him from his obtain position.
Green (LAL) dislodges the ball from McCollum (POR) before to making incidental contact to his arm.
Kuzma (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Green (LAL) swipes down and makes contact with the ball dislodging the ball away from Nurkic (POR).
Kuzma (LAL) places his hand momentarily to Anthony's (POR) and slides it off as he is setting the screen.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes marginal contact to James' (LAL) arm as he begins his drive to the basket.
Lillard (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball and makes marginal contact to Caruso's (LAL) side.
Lillard (POR) makes a marginal brush to Caruso's (LAL) arm prior to beginning his upward shooting motion.
Nurkic (POR) is already in Green's (LAL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Davis (LAL) briefly places his arm to McCollum's (POR) front and disengages defending his drive to the basket.
Davis (LAL) establishes his screening position in Trent's (POR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Caruso (LAL) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) during his drive.
Davis (LAL) is already in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path during the screen and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes marginal contact to Kuzma's (LAL) body after he releases his jump shot attempt.
